{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QLwMNgmGTV1WtFEYRc6Bv1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent analysis. Now I understand the full picture. I need to add `source_trust` as a signal in the composite retrieval scoring. The task says:\n\n> M2: Add `source_trust` signal to composite retrieval scoring in tapps-brain. Defaults: human=1.0, system=0.9, agent=0.7, inferred=0.5.\n\nLet me read the key files I need to modify:\n\n1. `retrieval.py` - Add source_trust as a component in composite scoring\n2. `profile.py` - Add source_trust config to ScoringConfig  \n3. Tests for the new feature\n\n\n4. Now I'm examining the actual implementation files to understand the current structure and where to integrate the source_trust signal.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":4183,"cache_read_input_tokens":29094,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":4183},"output_tokens":23,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1dfeb66a-ec06-46ac-b5f4-422c4dae48e2","uuid":"e9b4c690-077f-4070-bf86-30fc0eacba1f"}
